{
  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 22",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Arya IV</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/High_Heart\" title=\"High Heart\">High Heart</a> - <a href=\"/index.php/Acorn_Hall\" title=\"Acorn Hall\">Acorn Hall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n246 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_17\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 17\">Arya III</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_21\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 21\">Jaime III</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Arya IV</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_23\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 23\">Daenerys II</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_29\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 29\">Arya V</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">brotherhood without banners</a> searches for <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> sees the <a href=\"/index.php/Ghost_of_High_Heart\" title=\"Ghost of High Heart\">ghost of High Heart</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_22&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The outlaws first visit Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Lymond_Lychester\" title=\"Lymond Lychester\">Lymond Lychester</a> and then the <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_of_the_Leaves\" title=\"Lady of the Leaves\">Lady of the Leaves</a> in search of word on Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a>'s whereabouts. But none have seen him, only hearing rumors that he was dead—hanged once, killed by <a href=\"/index.php/Vargo_Hoat\" title=\"Vargo Hoat\">Vargo Hoat</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Amory_Lorch\" title=\"Amory Lorch\">Amory Lorch</a>, and twice by <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a> heard similar rumors at <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a>, but <a href=\"/index.php/Lem\" title=\"Lem\">Lem</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Tom_of_Sevenstreams\" title=\"Tom of Sevenstreams\">Tom</a> know that Beric is still alive. \n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Ravella_Smallwood_and_Arya_Stark_by_Amuelia.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/Ravella_Smallwood_and_Arya_Stark_by_Amuelia.png/300px-Ravella_Smallwood_and_Arya_Stark_by_Amuelia.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"403\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/Ravella_Smallwood_and_Arya_Stark_by_Amuelia.png/450px-Ravella_Smallwood_and_Arya_Stark_by_Amuelia.png 1.5x, /images/2/2b/Ravella_Smallwood_and_Arya_Stark_by_Amuelia.png 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Ravella_Smallwood_and_Arya_Stark_by_Amuelia.png\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Ravella and Arya Stark by Amuelia ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The outlaws plan to ransom Arya at <a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a> after they meet up with Beric and <a href=\"/index.php/Thoros_of_Myr\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Thoros of Myr\">Thoros of Myr</a>. They arrive at <a href=\"/index.php/High_Heart\" title=\"High Heart\">High Heart</a>, an ancient hill sacred to the <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a>. Thirty-one mighty <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood\" title=\"Weirwood\">weirwoods</a> had stood at the top of the hill, but only their stumps remained from after the <a href=\"/index.php/Andals\" title=\"Andals\">Andals</a> chopped them down. Arya can still feel the power of the place. An <a href=\"/index.php/Ghost_of_High_Heart\" title=\"Ghost of High Heart\">old dwarf woman</a> speaks in private to Lem, Tom, and <a href=\"/index.php/Greenbeard\" title=\"Greenbeard\">Greenbeard</a>, but Arya overhears the conversation. The woman has dreams while sleeping among the weirwood stumps, and tells them she had dreamed of \"a shadow with a burning heart killing a golden stag\";<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> of \"a man without a face, waiting on a swaying bridge, on his shoulder perched a drowned crow with seaweed hanging from its wings\";<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> and of \"a raging river and a woman that was a fish…dead with red tears on her cheeks, but when her eyes did open, I woke from terror.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>At <a href=\"/index.php/Acorn_Hall\" title=\"Acorn Hall\">Acorn Hall</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Ravella_Swann\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ravella Swann\">Lady Smallwood</a> informs them that Thoros had been through recently, and that <a href=\"/index.php/House_Karstark\" title=\"House Karstark\">Karstark</a> men were searching for the <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Kingslayer</a>. Arya and <a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a> go off to the smithy, and the former apprentice explains that Thoros was a charlatan, using regular swords with <a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire\" title=\"Wildfire\">wildfire</a> to make his flaming sword. After getting in a playful fight with Gendry, Arya tears a dress given to her by Lady Smallwood. As the Brotherhood is getting ready to leave, Lady Smallwood gives Arya clothes that had belonged to her now deceased son. Embarrassed by her actions, Arya apologizes to Lady Smallwood before leaving.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_22&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lymond_Lychester\" title=\"Lymond Lychester\">Lymond Lychester</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_of_the_Leaves\" title=\"Lady of the Leaves\">Lady of the Leaves</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Vargo_Hoat\" title=\"Vargo Hoat\">Vargo Hoat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Amory_Lorch\" title=\"Amory Lorch\">Amory Lorch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lem\" title=\"Lem\">Lem</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tom_of_Sevenstreams\" title=\"Tom of Sevenstreams\">Tom of Sevenstreams</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Thoros_of_Myr\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Thoros of Myr\">Thoros of Myr</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ghost_of_High_Heart\" title=\"Ghost of High Heart\">ghost of High Heart</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Greenbeard\" title=\"Greenbeard\">Greenbeard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Tully</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ravella_Swann\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ravella Swann\">Ravella Swann</a>, Lady Smallwood</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a>, the Kingslayer</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a></li></ul>\n</div>\t\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_22&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Riverrun\" title=\"Riverrun\">Riverrun</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Heart\" title=\"High Heart\">High Heart</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_forest\" title=\"Children of the forest\">children of the forest</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood\" title=\"Weirwood\">weirwood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Acorn_Hall\" title=\"Acorn Hall\">Acorn Hall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Karstark\" title=\"House Karstark\">House Karstark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire\" title=\"Wildfire\">wildfire</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_22&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">A likely reference to the death of <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">A likely reference to the death of <a href=\"/index.php/Balon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Balon Greyjoy\">Balon Greyjoy</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">A likely reference to the death of <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn Tully</a>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from AOL member vbkorik27 previously at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20080228051425/members.aol.com/vbkorik27/summary/legend.html\">[1]</a>.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tor.com/blogs/2013/01/a-read-of-ice-and-fire-a-storm-of-swords-part-13\">A Read of Ice and Fire: A Storm of Swords part 13</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter by Leigh Butler.</li>\n<li><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://slynt.blogspot.nl/2013/04/re-read-arya-iv-twice-in-tub.html\">Re-read Arya IV: Twice in the Tub</a>. Summary and analyses of the chapter in the course of a 10th reread by Slynt.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403121953\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.066 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.215 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 298/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1334/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 8528/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1507/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 871/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.140/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.28 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  197.253      1 -total\n 97.72%  192.765      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter_ASoS\n 97.37%  192.062      1 Template:Infobox_Chapter\n 97.00%  191.334      1 Template:Infobox\n  0.86%    1.687      1 Template:References\n  0.50%    0.984      2 Template:Columns\n  0.43%    0.858      2 Template:Work_color\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:5681-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403121953 and revision id 301448\n -->\n",
